quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  27,15,"Re ile ra fana ka tsebo ho Davida le Solomone; Ba re: “Lithoriso li be ho Allah, Ea re khethileng har’a makhabunyane a mangata a kholoang ho Eena!”"
  27,16,"Solomone e ne e le mojalefa oa Davida. A re: “Oho lona batho! Ruri! Re rutiloe puo ea linonyana, e bile re filoe nala ea lintho tsohle. Ruri! Sena ke molemo o hlakileng.”"
  27,17,"Mabotho a Masabonoeng le a batho le’a linonyana a kile a khobokana ‘moho kapel’a Solomone, eaba a hloptjoa ka mekhahlelo"
  27,18,"Ho fihlela a atametse haufinyane le phula ea bohloa, eaba bohloa bo le bong bo re: “Oho bohloa! Kenang ka matlung a lona esere mohlaope Solomone le mabotho a hae a tloha a le ripitla a sa le hlokomele.”"
  27,19,"Eaba salomone o’a bososela, a qaboloa ke puo ea bona, a re: “Mong`a ka! Ak’u ntaele hore ke be le teboho ka tlhohonolofatso eo U ntlhohonolofalitseng ka eona esita le batsoali ba ka, ke be ke etse tse lokileng tse ka U khahlisang, U be U nkenyeletse palong ea makhabunyane a Hau a lokileng.”"
  27,20,"Eaba o talima har’a linonyana, a nto re: “Ho tla joang hore e be ha ke bone hoopoe (mofuta o mong oa nonyana), kapa e be e har’a tse sieo"
  27,21,"Ruri! Ke tla e otla ka kotlo ea masisapelo, kapa ke e bolae, kantle leha eba e tla ntlela ka lebaka le totobetseng.”"
  27,22,"Empa ha ea ka ea senya nako ho ea pitsong, eaba e re: “ke fumane ntho eo uena u neng u sa e lemohe ho hang, ke tla ho uena ka litaba tse molemo tse tsoang Sheba"
  27,23,"“Ke fumane mosali a busa sechaba sa moo, e bile o nehiloe nala ea lintho tsohle, terone ea hae ke e makhabane"
  27,24,"“Ke fumane eena le sechaba sa hae ba khumamela letsatsi ntle ho Allah; Satane o entse hore mesebetsi ea bona e bonahale e khahleha mahlong a bona, e bile o ba sitisa ho kena tseleng ea ‘nete, hore ba tle ba tsamae ka nepo"
  27,25,"Ka ho ba khelosa ho se khumamele Allah, Eena Ea hlahisang Masabonoeng tsa maholimo le lefats’e, Ea bileng A tsebang tseo le li patang le tseo le li pepesang"
  27,26,Ke Allah; ha ho `Mopi e mong ntle ho Eena! – Eena Mong`a Terone e Hloahloeng
  27,27,"Eaba Solomone o re: “Re tla bona haeba feela u buoa ‘nete, kapa leshano"
  27,28,“Tsamaea le
  27,29,"Mofumahali oa Sheba a re: “Oho lona matona! Ruri! Ke amohetse Lengolo le hlomphehang"
  27,30,"Le tsoa ho Solomone, le baleha joana: “Ka lebitso la Allah, Ea Tletseng Lereko, Ea Mohau o Khaphatsehang"
  27,31,"“Se ikhohomose khahlano le ‘na, empa atamela ho ‘na joaloka ba ithapalatsang.”"